=Description=

PiggyBee is a collaborative shipping network, connecting people who want to get or ship something with travelers.
It can be anything from (or to) anywhere. The platform also offers eco-friendly freecycling to get rid of things. Ship anything for free. Crowdsourced delivery. Collaborative shipping.

    
